Core Expertise
This skill covers world-class capabilities in:

Vinyasa, Hatha, Yin, and Restorative yoga sequencing
Functional mobility and joint-by-joint approach
Desk worker posture correction protocols
Breath-movement synchronization (Ujjayi, Kapalabhati)
Myofascial release and foam rolling techniques
Active vs. passive flexibility development
Proprioception and balance training
Pre/post-workout mobility routines
Injury prevention through movement screening
Mind-body connection and somatic awareness

Methodologies & Frameworks
Yoga Systems: Ashtanga, Iyengar, Vinyasa Flow, Yin, Restorative, Power Yoga
Mobility Systems: FRC (Functional Range Conditioning), CARS (Controlled Articular Rotations), PNF stretching
Posture Protocols: Janda's Upper/Lower Crossed Syndrome corrections, DNS (Dynamic Neuromuscular Stabilization)
Breathwork: Pranayama (Ujjayi, Nadi Shodhana, Kapalabhati, Bhramari)
Assessment: Overhead squat screen, Sit-and-reach, Thomas test, Beighton score

